{
  "_aboutme": [
    "ABOUTME: Curated scope map for the derived item schema: every Class value on in-scope",
    "ABOUTME: records maps to a domain/type/slots entry (or an explicit exclusion), per category.",
    "Drift guard (scripts/build_derived.py): a record in a scoped category whose Class is absent",
    "from `classes` fails the build loudly; `domain: null` entries are deliberate exclusions and",
    "are only counted. `categories` lists every records/items/* prefix with the domains allowed",
    "there ([] = structural, out of scope); an unknown records/items/* prefix also fails the",
    "build. Categories outside records/items/ are opt-in only: the four listed carry the",
    "grimtools-visible quest-reward wearables (e.g. Wilhelm's Wondrous Wargem); dev sandbox,",
    "fx, and NPC cosmetic armor stay out by omission.",
    "Slots are multi-valued (R15): one-handed and two-handed weapons occupy main and off hand,",
    "shields and caster off-hands the off hand only."
  ],
